        <p>This table directly visualizes key metrics presented in the product overview, offering an immediate, at-a-glance summary of operational performance.[1] In a one-pager format, visual summaries are paramount for quick comprehension. It effectively communicates workload dynamics and performance against targets, reinforcing the module's promise of providing a "full picture" without requiring extensive text. The inclusion of "Trend" highlights the dynamic nature of ECC operations, which the Intelligent Analyst module is designed to track and optimize.</p>

